{"tid":645110,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇都係啱啱分手嘅人可以分享下點放低另一半","createTime":"2018-04-27T20:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T10:06:54.000Z","uid":27003,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b69e820e99a57846275a1987888477f4bcd7f0dd","tid":645110,"uid":27003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T20:17:04.000Z","msg":"拍左拖三年幾<br />\n自己本身內向撚無乜朋友<br />\n全幅心機放係佢到<br />\n散左之後日日流流長都唔知做咩好<br />\n最痛苦係日日訓醒都會想當無事發生過咁照搵佢<br />\n開Whatsapp 先發現已經唔再係以前咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣落去真係好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe663bcfd141dbb3eb5b83b53a1ebe8733145e3","tid":645110,"uid":89665,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T20:20:13.000Z","msg":"做其他野分散注意力"},{"pid":"65b999846a508f50375b1db8c7238b14343e9576","tid":645110,"uid":16772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T20:22:13.000Z","msg":"發覺愈嚟愈多拍緊拖既男人已經漸漸失去自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/644236/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/644236/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9a42ce84d7d23b7641fcd36460c89df30d0f09f5","tid":645110,"uid":166763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T20:27:45.000Z","msg":"同路人 巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘗試慢慢搵返自己  停止留戀過去<br />\n望將來<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c2a6e7487ea5e7dbb48fe76e8abdd47acf7fff","tid":645110,"uid":98078,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T20:59:45.000Z","msg":"瘋狂做 gym <br />\n好多時對方會捨得同你分手 因為你個人唔夠吸引<br />\n<br />\n做多d野 令自己更好 下次會遇到更好既"},{"pid":"9ffd40ad84c0f62b2830ad73a9e3d17fbb8a4cc3","tid":645110,"uid":20908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T21:08:20.000Z","msg":"岩岩分手<br />\n睇完分手果段野之後<br />\n喊到仆街，好多回憶突然湧上心頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b7c83921f0f0b8a6558f3120746b1d30ed4b3b","tid":645110,"uid":8482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T06:22:08.000Z","msg":"學下其他野<br />\n例如學西班牙文呀<br />\n增值下自己<br />\n咁先有吸引力<br />\n為下一段感情再作準備<br />\n<br />\n去聽下葡萄成熟時鼓勵自己<br />\n一定有個某某等緊你依杯紅酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：啱啱散咗一個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375e66d7e2f38c2bc54ac3fe9307f601b23696f5","tid":645110,"uid":92488,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T08:27:01.000Z","msg":"話我老套都係個一句<br />\n時間可以沖淡一切<br />\n我都被分手個幾月 已經好過上個月 但仲係會有時諗起佢掛住佢 但起碼肯去死心 因為已經知道佢再唔係我  唔會可以再一齊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16de8b089d97498f110a7c98b548ca6da3f8c7c","tid":645110,"uid":14298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T08:43:12.000Z","msg":"搵返自己既興趣<br />\n之前拍拖無晒時間做自己想做既野<br />\n分咗手唔開心咗一排之後 我反而更加珍惜依加既時間<br />\n過多一排試下約下其他女仔出街 到時又係另一條好漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb26c5062aa48c5c7709b31247feb7a3c2940eb","tid":645110,"uid":89368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T09:56:01.000Z","msg":"拍左5年半分左（兩個月前嘅事，本身諗住結婚），但3日後諗通晒，覺得自己值得擁有更好，而且段感情我處理得問心無愧，反正都要向前行，所以努力認識下一個更好。<br />\n<br />\n（當然頭三日未諗通果時都好辛苦，唔開心到胃口都冇，一日食半碗粥咁）加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66369d311c90f3501f00d13eab8f8730949fe0a2","tid":645110,"uid":183856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T10:06:54.000Z","msg":"揾過個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}